        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>Founded with a passion for quality and a vision for accessible luxury, Sole Haven has grown from a small startup to a trusted name in footwear for both men and women. Our journey began with a simple idea: to create a haven where everyone can find their perfect pair of shoes, regardless of their style or budget.</p>
